  • SVG Ionicons
  • SVG Stockholm Duotone Icons

Font Awesome

The iconic font and CSS toolkit.

<i class="fab fa-2x fa-canadian-maple-leaf text-primary"></i>
<i class="far fa-2x fa-check-circle text-success"></i>
<i class="fas fa-2x fa-bell text-darkblue"></i>
Put any icon inside a circle with .icon-circle
<div class="icon-circle icon-circle-xs bg-pistachio text-dark">
  <i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h fa-xs"></i>
</div>

</div>
